{
  "info": {
    "name": "SkillFlow AI v2 \u2014 Backend",
    "description": "Local demo API for the SkillFlow AI fresher & PM dashboards.\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}} (default http://10.0.128.20:8000). Swagger: {{base_url}}/docs\n\nAUTH: Call **Auth > Login (Fresher)** and **Auth > Login (PM)** first \u2014 their test scripts store {{fresher_token}} and {{pm_token}} automatically. Every other request sends the right bearer token via a header.\n\nRUN ORDER (Collection Runner friendly): Login Fresher -> Login PM -> Create Roadmap (stores {{roadmap_id}}) -> Create Daily Report (stores {{report_id}}) -> ... -> Complete Roadmap -> Create Final Report -> PM Dashboard.\n\nThe backend performs NO AI generation; it stores and serves the AI results the frontend submits.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "description": "",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "health"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Liveness check. No auth."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Demo Reset",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/demo/reset",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "demo",
                "reset"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Idempotently recreates the seeded demo dataset (users, assignment, profile, sample roadmap, sample daily report). Safe to run before every demo."
